data.description: Gorgeous, Newly Constructed, and Grand are ideal to introduce this 4 Bedroom 2.5 Bathroom oasis .  Featuring a lavish kitchen with ample dining space, an oversized island with extra storage, 42 inch cabinets, the glass sliding doors allowowing lots of natural sunlight, large living room plus a den/bonus room, laundry room, spacious bedrooms and a Master suite with a private  bathrooom.    Schedule an appointment today to see additional amenities and tour the area.  Home is in a central location with easy access to Philadelphia/New York and beyond via I95, I295, Route 1 and 29; multiple train stations within 1-5 miles, Trenton/Mercer airport; Government Offices; shopping/entertainment.  Submit your offer today!  NOTE: UPGRADES ARE AVAILABLE AND WILL BE CONSIDERED WITH AN EXECUTED  AND ADDITIONAL COST DEPENDING ON THE REQUEST.  10 Year New Home Warranty.
